Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.79,0:00:03.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.46,0:00:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.21,0:00:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经是谈论这种话题的季节了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.27,0:00:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够不去想自已不愿想起的事情就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.87,0:00:18.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的头脑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.67,0:00:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.76,0:00:21.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不送给令大人巧克力了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.75,0:00:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年都送
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.64,0:00:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 相对于每年都变得更大的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.75,0:00:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她拿什么送给我才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.01,0:00:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 令大人每年也要送给你礼物吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.39,0:00:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令大人与她的外表相反 内心相当的女孩子气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.60,0:00:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作糕点的手艺更是让专业人员都甘拜下风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.28,0:00:46.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身体也变好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.22,0:00:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用市面贩卖的巧克力大概是不行的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.49,0:00:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一定要是巧克力呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用其它的东西也不错啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.63,0:00:55.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要是亲手做的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.65,0:01:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在温暖着由乃同学的这些东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.56,0:01:05.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部都是令大人亲手做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.82,0:01:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能给你做参考真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.27,0:01:11.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于你想送给祥子大人的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.03,0:01:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我和祥子大人初次的情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.83,0:01:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聚集在玛莉亚的庭院里的少女们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:23.43,0:01:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也带着天使般无垢的笑容 穿越与身同高的门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.74,0:01:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覆盖住纯洁身心的是深色的制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.50,0:01:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让裙子的摺痕乱掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.26,0:01:39.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让白色的水手服领结外翻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.48,0:01:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒缓的行走成了这里的习俗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.44,0:01:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,私立莉莉安女学园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.96,0:01:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是少女的花园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.20,0:03:25.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}吃惊的巧克力·前篇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.66,0:03:30.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的吧 志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么呀 佑巳同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.49,0:03:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是我至少情人节还是知道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.92,0:03:40.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2月14日 瓦伦丁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.34,0:03:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是记念殉教的意大利圣人的节日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.18,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过与巧克力好像是没什么关系就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.21,0:03:51.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 你不送给白蔷薇大人巧克力了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.80,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对志摩子同学来说也是初次的情人节吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想都没想过呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.71,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能给你做参考真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.88,0:04:05.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算这样 问我也是没用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.95,0:04:09.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很不凑巧既没有姐姐也没有妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.47,0:04:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起原来所想的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.62,0:04:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节也许会是一个很麻烦的活动呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.20,0:04:17.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没法依靠由乃同学与志摩子同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.70,0:04:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其它人里该问谁才好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么一定要是一年级生呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.82,0:04:22.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.75,0:04:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是二年级生还是三年级生\n可也是体验过一年级生的生活啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.51,0:04:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 三年级生正忙于应付考试
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.61,0:04:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够问的人就只有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.99,0:04:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送给姐姐的巧克力？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 去年是送过 怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.91,0:04:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.12,0:04:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想能够听听做一下参考就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.61,0:04:45.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是一个很简朴的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.53,0:04:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹心苦味巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.77,0:04:50.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以将制作方法写给你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.45,0:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夹心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.45,0:04:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没法成为参考啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.37,0:04:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我自满
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.74,0:05:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在做糕点上除了曾做过\n烤面圈的定型外其它什么都不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.58,0:05:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前途多难啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.24,0:05:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.41,0:05:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花蕾们的巧克力在哪里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.05,0:05:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.72,0:05:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新闻部的情人节企划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位花蕾将在校内藏起亲手做的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.64,0:05:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.12,0:05:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.59,0:05:30.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳 情况还很混乱 你稍微安静一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.30,0:05:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.70,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然你特意来访 但我们无法协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.49,0:05:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.46,0:05:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.48,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是想改善新闻部的形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.06,0:05:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞧 这也是很能为一般学生们所接受的企划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.04,0:05:48.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太勉强了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.13,0:05:52.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 将食物长时间存放就是一个问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.10,0:05:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且将巧克力堂堂正正地\n带进学校也不知是否行得通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.46,0:06:00.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 老师们也说了情人节就睁一只眼闭一只眼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.19,0:06:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.65,0:06:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,单方面被强迫接受的礼物只是一种麻烦而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.16,0:06:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说祥子大人不喜欢情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.61,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到全校里充满了巧克力的味道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.89,0:06:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说祥子大人也讨厌巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.87,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么如果改变宝物的话 能否同意参加这个企划呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.93,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将手写的情人节卡片藏起来 红色 黄色 白色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.08,0:06:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来一开始就不是想要巧克力 而是盯着卡片呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.13,0:06:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再把那些卡片做为附加奖的兑换卷如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.03,0:06:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,附加奖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.54,0:06:42.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与花蕾们的半天约会权
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.59,0:06:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.86,0:06:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是山百合会主办的 那么我们就不能参加了是吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.39,0:06:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 就是说只能让我以外的其它人与姐姐约会？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反对反对 绝对反对！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.15,0:07:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将个人的私有时间商品化是不对的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 山百合会全员一致拒绝这个企划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.06,0:07:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然因为由乃同学的竭力反对 这个企划被驳回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.43,0:07:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.51,0:07:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对新闻部的回答决定了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.00,0:07:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连黄蔷薇大人也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.47,0:07:43.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐们聚在一起下了命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.59,0:07:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就算不是心甘情愿也只有同意了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.94,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是跟以前一样 头脑顽固呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.40,0:07:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,选择了这样一个顽固脑袋作妹妹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.40,0:07:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是哪一位呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.15,0:07:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.29,0:07:59.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才希望你的头脑能变得稍微灵活一点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.37,0:08:03.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和普通学生们的交流 不是很好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.47,0:08:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在选了佑巳作妹妹后 脸上的表情已经好看多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.76,0:08:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.68,0:08:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一回合 祥子大人的K.O.败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.84,0:08:18.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.22,0:08:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.19,0:08:22.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要说什么 你明白的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会协助新闻部的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.47,0:08:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.56,0:08:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.50,0:08:35.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种向人施压的方式 不觉得太过份了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令也是的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.24,0:08:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在和令说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.61,0:08:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望没有关系的人不要插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.42,0:08:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不明白吗 由乃越是认真就越会让姐姐干劲十足
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.92,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差得远呢 由乃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.66,0:08:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二回合 令大人与由乃同学放弃比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.11,0:08:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三回合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.89,0:09:02.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这么回事 加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.67,0:09:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.76,0:09:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣大人的不战而胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.12,0:09:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳好像闷闷不乐呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.75,0:09:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.53,0:09:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真羡慕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.94,0:09:22.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明祥子大人只要能向我笑一笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就能感到安心的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.90,0:09:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢各位欣然允诺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.46,0:09:32.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡片的隐藏地点\n应局限于学生们平常能出入的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.89,0:09:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而对特定人员有利的教室或活动室 我认为应该排除在外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.24,0:09:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～ 最差劲的情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.53,0:09:48.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是花蕾的妹妹 我应该也能参加的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.62,0:09:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次活动 能否改为只有花蕾们参加企划呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.80,0:09:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.55,0:09:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 花蕾以外的人都能参加寻宝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.69,0:10:04.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对你们两人来说 也不是件坏事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.40,0:10:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你们不想赌上那几百分之一的概率
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.28,0:10:09.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得到与姐姐们约会的机会吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.49,0:10:10.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.89,0:10:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.16,0:10:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有异议
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.06,0:10:18.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花蕾们的妹妹们能参加的话 也可成为很好的话题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.02,0:10:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是为了这种时候的杂活 才需要妹妹帮忙的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.05,0:10:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人一点都没想到要与我约会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.12,0:10:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后我还有一个请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.51,0:10:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请在卡片的隐藏地点中加上蔷薇馆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.09,0:10:39.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐… 为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.11,0:10:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里本来是学生会议室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.39,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知何时蔷薇大人们被神圣化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.00,0:10:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都不再靠近这里了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.13,0:10:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 在毕业之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.81,0:10:52.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想看看蔷薇馆里普通学生们喧闹的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可是我的梦想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.70,0:10:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.37,0:11:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最后的情人节里 将最好的一天作为礼物送给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.34,0:11:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟总是焦虑不安的我不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓉子大人与祥子大人牢固地联系着彼此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.74,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会找到令的卡片的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.85,0:11:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没什么信心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.07,0:11:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.09,0:11:26.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓姐妹 就是有只有身为姐妹才有的好处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.19,0:11:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.93,0:11:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为充分地理解对方的兴趣和嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以总能找到寻找卡片的线索吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.73,0:11:34.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.78,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要待在身边 很可能会不经意地透露出一些提示呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.19,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 是什么时候隐藏的从态度上就可以看出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.16,0:11:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有好处的不是姐妹 而是由乃同学才对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.71,0:11:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到情人节之前 这种情况会很常见吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.97,0:11:55.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,待在蔷薇馆里也变得有点辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.91,0:12:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人成为红蔷薇大人后 会变得更忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.82,0:12:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 祥子大人与我的距离或许会变得更远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.83,0:12:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由乃 让你久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.37,0:12:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.99,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见 佑巳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.61,0:12:12.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.88,0:12:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.18,0:12:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.59,0:12:21.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要成为姐姐的负担
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.75,0:12:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要让姐姐担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.21,0:12:31.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是花蕾们在那边交谈 让你感到不安了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.67,0:12:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天色已经这么暗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.83,0:12:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.35,0:12:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.60,0:12:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不出口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.73,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到不安并不是因为黑暗 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.62,0:13:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学 你真的什么也不知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.43,0:13:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,花蕾们准备把卡片放在哪里什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.73,0:13:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.51,0:13:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.84,0:13:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么提示也好呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.39,0:13:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们也要参加活动 所以真的什么也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.91,0:13:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.57,0:13:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们去图书馆了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.49,0:13:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 以活泼为优点的佑巳同学竟会叹气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.11,0:13:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说来 对妹妹们来说现在是很不开心的状况了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.80,0:13:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.34,0:13:32.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佑巳同学不去图书馆吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.84,0:13:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,午休时大家好像都去查有关巧克力的书了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.49,0:13:39.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人看起来很讨厌巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.60,0:13:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人在圣诞节\n可是吃了一大块圣诞巧克力蛋糕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.68,0:13:46.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黄蔷薇的花蕾亲手做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.13,0:13:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么\n也就是只反感在情人节送巧克力这个风俗了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.23,0:13:57.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是哪一边 对我来说都是一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.85,0:14:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在情人节送巧克力的乐趣消失无踪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.64,0:14:05.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而喜欢的人又可能会与别人去约会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.15,0:14:07.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒真是让人提不起劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.99,0:14:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在蔷薇馆里也无容身之所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.15,0:14:12.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教室里的话题又全都是情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.29,0:14:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望能对你有所帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.04,0:14:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令的特制配方也在里面啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.36,0:14:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太谢谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.92,0:14:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.90,0:14:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,令大人干劲十足啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.25,0:14:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说\n大家常被其美少年般的外表所迷惑而未注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但她其实真的是一个很爱照顾别人的好心人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.99,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对 毕竟能和那个由乃同学好好相处了这么长时间嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.47,0:14:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么吃惊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.43,0:14:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.14,0:14:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 我告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.53,0:14:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是要商量关于情人节的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.84,0:14:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是有什么事情吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.83,0:14:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.70,0:15:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子大人心情好像也很不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.86,0:15:05.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就别在这儿闲聊浪费时间 快点回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.96,0:15:07.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子 别用那种口气说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.07,0:15:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我强把佑巳带来这里的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.36,0:15:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.95,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 能顺道去菊组把这个交给由乃吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.10,0:15:30.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把巧克力交给\N心情那么恶劣的祥子大人果然是太勉强了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在迷惑中到了情人节的前一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.67,0:15:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请保佑情人节能成为我最好的一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.67,0:15:59.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 差不多也是合唱部的练习时间了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.82,0:16:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系 反正大家还没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.63,0:16:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节看来很麻烦的样子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.15,0:16:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对花蕾们的妹妹来说 特别是今年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.95,0:16:10.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.32,0:16:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.36,0:16:17.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也准备送给白蔷薇大人巧克力喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.22,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.36,0:16:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情人节不正是适合传达心意的日子吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.67,0:16:24.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明对白蔷薇大人做过失礼的事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.69,0:16:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个越打越坚强的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.64,0:16:29.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为白蔷薇大人很体贴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.78,0:16:32.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来不会拒绝收到的巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 红蔷薇的花蕾可就麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.83,0:16:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.64,0:16:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年的情人节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.27,0:16:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祥子同学摆出一副厌烦的神色 将收到的堆积如山的巧克力全退了回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.41,0:16:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.86,0:16:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我觉得那也算一种体贴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退回去了吗？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.20,0:16:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没法送给祥子大人巧克力吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也好好地享受节日如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.90,0:17:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.09,0:17:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是烦恼还是迷茫一定都会成为美好的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.36,0:17:08.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去年只是一个旁观者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.48,0:17:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而今年一定要创造能带去意大利的美好回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以佑巳同学也要努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.64,0:17:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,静大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.65,0:17:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寻宝那方面也加油吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.76,0:17:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.78,0:17:24.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也希望尽可能由最能理解我的人找到我的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.76,0:17:25.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.90,0:17:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说也许无法将巧克力送出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.28,0:17:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这次活动一定要加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.16,0:17:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要最先找到红色的卡片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.23,0:17:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为妹妹 我想成为最理解姐姐的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.37,0:17:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话 也许就能让祥子大人稍微认可我一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.59,0:18:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是小刚狐吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.06,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.26,0:18:13.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.31,0:18:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是佑巳的美学吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.81,0:18:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近你都是趁大家不注意时\n悄悄地干完杂活才回去的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.90,0:18:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是觉得坐久了想干点什么而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.11,0:18:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没有挑三捡四的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.51,0:18:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且向佑巳的自我满足上泼冷水也太不知趣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.22,0:18:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做错了什么吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.71,0:18:38.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就觉得现在的佑巳总是在心里想突出自已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.35,0:18:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不太好说明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.35,0:18:42.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自我满足？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.84,0:18:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.07,0:18:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.89,0:18:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.77,0:18:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人在志愿校的考试中合格了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.10,0:19:00.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为想第一个将此事告诉志摩子同学 才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.14,0:19:02.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不需要什么巧克力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对白蔷薇姐妹来说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.88,0:19:07.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不必拘于形式 也能传达彼此的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.61,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 小刚狐不向我祝贺吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜您
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.96,0:19:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.89,0:19:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 真是辛苦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.93,0:19:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直没准备念大学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.13,0:19:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应试复习也是从今年才开始的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.37,0:19:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.30,0:19:29.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个月的复习就合格了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.88,0:19:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然对还不知结果的江利子与蓉子很失礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但从明天开始就可以好好地放松享受了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.51,0:19:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人也要参加寻宝吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.61,0:19:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么有趣的事怎么可以袖手旁观呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.21,0:19:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 至少得让你尖叫一声“嘎～”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前一阵我就说过了吧 佑巳～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.24,0:19:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白蔷薇大人 请住手啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.20,0:19:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.99,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.19,0:20:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贵安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.11,0:20:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天的眼神特别的严厉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.52,0:20:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相当的开心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.55,0:20:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 刚才白蔷薇大人在这里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.52,0:20:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有白蔷薇大人在你就会很开心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.76,0:20:21.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.00,0:20:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从什么时候开始 你变得讨厌我到连脸都不想看的程度呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.96,0:20:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.92,0:20:30.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌姐姐？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.75,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.40,0:20:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么为什么要避开我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.81,0:20:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避开？ 怎么可能…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.87,0:20:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是避开了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.89,0:20:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最初我还以为因为我是花蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.43,0:20:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为了公平地参加情人节企划才避开我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.32,0:20:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 你却跟往常一样地接近令与志摩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.40,0:20:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.23,0:20:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使来到蔷薇馆 你也会在我来之前就回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.82,0:20:59.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是要从我面前逃走似的避得远远的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.89,0:21:01.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早也是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.25,0:21:03.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今早？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.52,0:21:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在圣母玛莉亚之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.90,0:21:07.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像为了避开我似的走开了不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.36,0:21:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 今早有和祥子大人相遇过吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.91,0:21:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且 我也并没有特别去避开什么的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.43,0:21:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有想说的话就好好地给我说出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.60,0:21:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为我不想成为姐姐的妨碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.69,0:21:24.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才只做了扫除就回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.83,0:21:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 那不就是白蔷薇大人所说的自我满足吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.11,0:21:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不说话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.65,0:21:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你内心深处的话语为什么就不能向我倾诉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.96,0:21:39.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样的话我什么都无法明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.80,0:21:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.69,0:21:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,志摩子 过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.36,0:22:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管发生什么事 我都不可能会讨厌祥子大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.61,0:22:05.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这些话无法说出口 却只换来泪水的流淌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.41,0:22:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢的人的轮廓在眼前渐渐地模糊
